          <p class="mt-4 text-body-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-text-dark-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">Our four-step process ensures a seamless journey from concept to creation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary via-accent to-primary hidden md:block"></div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-12 scroll-reveal-stagger">
            <div class="scroll-reveal md:text-right">
              <div class="relative inline-block group">
                <span class="absolute -right-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 h-5 w-5 rounded-full bg-primary hidden md:block ring-4 ring-primary/20 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300"></span>
                <h3 class="font-display text-heading-3 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-text-dark-primary">1. Discovery</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed">We dive deep into your goals to architect the perfect solution.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="scroll-reveal"></div>
            
            <div class="scroll-reveal"></div>
            <div class="scroll-reveal md:text-left">
              <div class="relative inline-block group">
                <span class="absolute -left-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 h-5 w-5 rounded-full bg-accent hidden md:block ring-4 ring-accent/20 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300"></span>
                <h3 class="font-display text-heading-3 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-text-dark-primary">2. Spell Blueprint</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed">Crafting intuitive interfaces and robust system designs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="scroll-reveal md:text-right">
              <div class="relative inline-block group">
                <span class="absolute -right-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 h-5 w-5 rounded-full bg-primary hidden md:block ring-4 ring-primary/20 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300"></span>
                <h3 class="font-display text-heading-3 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-text-dark-primary">3. Summoning</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed">Our senior developers bring the designs to life with clean, efficient code.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="scroll-reveal"></div>
            
            <div class="scroll-reveal"></div>
            <div class="scroll-reveal md:text-left">
              <div class="relative inline-block group">
                <span class="absolute -left-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 h-5 w-5 rounded-full bg-accent hidden md:block ring-4 ring-accent/20 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300"></span>
                <h3 class="font-display text-heading-3 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-text-dark-primary">4. Ongoing Magic</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed">We ensure a smooth launch and provide continuous support and enhancements.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="testimonials" class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark py-24 scroll-reveal">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-display text-heading-1 font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-text-dark-primary">What Our Clients Say</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-body-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-text-dark-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">Hear from those who've experienced our magic firsthand.</p>
        </div>
        <TestimonialCarousel />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="pricing" class="bg-neutral-silver dark:bg-surface-dark py-24 scroll-reveal">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="font-display text-heading-1 font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-text-dark-primary">Choose Your Spell</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-body-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-text-dark-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">Flexible plans to suit your project's needs, from quick enchantments to grand magical creations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center scroll-reveal-stagger">
          <div class="scroll-reveal bg-background-light dark:bg-surface-darker p-8 rounded-xl shadow-card border border-gray-200 dark:border-border-dark card-hover">
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-text-dark-primary">Starter Spell</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-text-dark-secondary">For small projects &amp; prototypes.</p>
            <p class="mt-6 font-display text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-text-dark-primary">$5k<span class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">/mo</span></p>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-text-dark-secondary">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 text-lg">check</span>
